Jangan ambil, tolong!

183
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:30,990
Tuanku, tolonglah!

184
00:10:30,990 --> 00:10:31,755
Manman...

185
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:34,230
Saya mesti patuh.

186
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:36,190
Ayah!

187
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:39,977
Tuanku!

188
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:41,540
Tuanku, semuanya salah saya!

189
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:42,590
Tolong, lepaskan ayah saya!

190
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:43,260
Saya merayu!

191
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,044
Manman.

192
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,590
Saya telah mengecewakan kamu.

193
00:10:47,710 --> 00:10:48,260
Tidak.

194
