Saya tak dapat menjaga kamu.

195
00:10:49,710 --> 00:10:50,260
Tidak!

196
00:10:54,110 --> 00:10:55,710
Saya layak dihukum seribu kali mati.

197
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:59,310
Saya hanya mohon Tuanku lepaskan Manman.

198
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:00,540
Ayah!

199
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:01,430
Dia tidak bersalah.

200
00:11:02,350 --> 00:11:03,422
Laksanakan hukuman.

201
00:11:05,350 --> 00:11:06,260
Ayah! Ayah!

202
